{"tid":1469824,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"要贏，首先要認清敵人驚啲乜！！","createTime":"2019-08-14T03:12:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T07:24:51.000Z","uid":232766,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"9dfe7691c1e9f2c23764cbf880e10c781ec79c99","tid":1469824,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:12:57.000Z","msg":"中共其實無嘢驚，<br />\n除咗：<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>國。際。輿。論</strong></span>！<br />\n<br />\n因為，只有國際輿論先有機會損害<strong><ins>北京政權</ins></strong>，<br />\n而<strong>北京政權先係所有嘢嘅始作俑者</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n坦白講，莫講話癱瘓機場做唔到同北京「攬炒」，<br />\n就算你癱瘓股市、摧毀香港樓價，<br />\n陪你「攬炒」嘅頂多係本地高官同權貴，<br />\n對幕後嘅北京政權影響唔大、甚至極微。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">共產黨方針係每當「管治威信」受到威協，<br />\n任何嘢都可以犧牲，<br />\n寧願放棄部分權貴利益，都要大力鎮壓，<br />\n最多之後再補償班權貴。</span><br />\n<br />\n所以，嚴格嚟講，<br />\n我哋喺香港做嘅所有（重複：係所有）動作，<br />\n動作本身佢哋都唔會點驚，<br />\n只會見招刷招，<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>反正佢哋有無限資源，</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>而香港嘅抗爭者拉一個少一個</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n但一「辣著」國際輿論，又唔同講法，<br />\n好似 6.12 咁。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">佢哋點解要驚國際輿論？<br />\n因為國際輿論除咗為中共喺外交、貿易上帶來諸多不便外，<br />\n仲可能會引發國際制裁。<br />\n當國內經濟受創（依家已經危危乎），<br />\n民生不保，呢個政權就會不穩。</span><br />\n<br />\n今次反送中政府肯暫緩修例，<br />\n大家都好清楚，係純粹因為 6.12 太核突、<br />\n國際譴責，再加上 G20 先會「讓步」，<br />\n否則，我哋 200 萬人出多嚟 10 次、<br />\n佔領多 10 次立法會，都未必有用。<br />\n<br />\n我唔係咩民意撚，<br />\n我相信真正嘅香港人根本從來都無割過蓆，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>但國際民意、輿論，我哋一定唔可以輸，<br />\n呢個係我哋暫時唯一可以依賴嘅反擊利器。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>所以，我建議可以繼續做機場和理飛文宣，<br />\n向全世界宣傳香港嘅困境，<br />\n但唔需要（亦唔好）主動阻人出入境，<br />\n亦唔需要癱瘓機場（除非人數多，「自然癱瘓」），<br />\n因為咁做係確實為外國人帶來不便。<br />\n佢哋係我哋盟友，唔係敵人，<br />\n你搞佢哋、為佢哋帶來不便，<br />\n莫講話佢哋唔明點解，香港人自己都未必明。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n以上都係點點意見俾行動者參考、討論，<br />\n不割蓆、不指責、不分化、不篤灰！<br />\n<br />\n（後記：其實中共仲有一樣嘢驚，<br />\n就係國內革命，但呢樣比較遙遠，不贅。）<br />\n<br />\n認同的話請幫推。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"567ea849eda12630224dd36f904409527fb64ad6","tid":1469824,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:13:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"eaa3daad71d1e45b9f3b41c7b010f4951d1f37c6","tid":1469824,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:13:52.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2130cfdbae5e698fc8edb39b6e894733ef8d156e","tid":1469824,"uid":42250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:13:56.000Z","msg":"黑 警 機 場 拔 槍 指 嚇 示 威 者 ！ 同 你 逐 格 睇 暨 聽 日 文 宣 方 向<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1467801\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1467801</a>"},{"pid":"b8389c69370f6b478a00aff8374949194653d6d5","tid":1469824,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:14:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"75c82cb18922a33e18255ef59d0eb2a3a3b929f7","tid":1469824,"uid":84457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:14:42.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"53011d16eaf12194a26f23400489f0e76edb78c4","tid":1469824,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:15:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/6c057950ed65cc1fac07eb212cfe3471/tumblr_nfv4w34Uby1qcbtvqo5_250.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F6c057950ed65cc1fac07eb212cfe3471%2Ftumblr_nfv4w34Uby1qcbtvqo5_250.gif&h=74060c35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[輸出革命］由今日起，不叫港獨，改叫「廣獨」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1447204\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1447204</a><br />\n<br />\n其實我地係唔需要洗佢地腦，甚至唔需要接觸任何人，要做既野只需要貼去多大陸人既地方都係廣獨／粵獨poster就得....<br />\n只要將廣獨思想文宣貼到通街都係，中共知道左就自然唔敢放自由行落黎<br />\n將廣獨思想輸出從而增加中共管治成本同時減少自由行黎香港！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7nZFbOE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7nZFbOE.png&h=4fd8318f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴打可以用下面條link去印，set左a5 size<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1qG8N4AsnroP--EywjjvBhkhWvLzeCzeR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D1qG8N4AsnroP--EywjjvBhkhWvLzeCzeR&d=0oBAxbMcX4V1PEKlHKxm0RZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=cc7ec9db\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=1qG8N4AsnroP--EywjjvBhkhWvLzeCzeR</a>"},{"pid":"5e047b264c6011605e16e57696e7a798cc4107a0","tid":1469824,"uid":274425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:15:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e61f033f40dc066c35e75600b6130787c27a525b","tid":1469824,"uid":221360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:15:51.000Z","msg":"大家停一停，唔好再話自己手足喇。。激動既有佢激動既原因，加上星期日之後有邊個唔嬲呀？大家可唔可以係唔同身份角度諗下呢？大家都係香港人，矛頭都係一致，對準政府呀！！唔該大家理智d諗諗再行動，其實有冇鬼都係一樣，睇返場合睇返當時既形勢處境，亦都係旅客個角度去諗下啦。尋日我地真係有唔岩既地方架，試諗下尋日d機係未取消既情況，旅客delay佢地上唔到機，班機照飛，錢照袋，旅客比左錢冇得搭機係咪會燥呀？？唔該各位手足理性少少，唔好比d唔理性既人帶到啦。。既然我地人手唔夠多，做唔到癱瘓行動，咁咪轉第二個策略，做宣傳，等夜晚多d手足入黎做返前一日做既野囉，而家比人唔理性既帶風向做過激既事，你覺得邊個最開心呀？林鄭呀！！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">btw重點：唔好再話自己手足喇，咁做都做左，一齊諗下計點解決／舒緩呢件事啦好冇？</span></span></strong><br />\n仲有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">獨立思考</span></strong></span>！！大家都係聰明人，比我聰明100倍都唔止。"},{"pid":"b540d4a195be1a1f6086aa03bad91120bcccf4ba","tid":1469824,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:17:10.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"33c5adf80f5dea472e36c8b4254fc3c8f41b9e47","tid":1469824,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:19:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0001619407dc0b73e682f6631069c25f4dd56862","tid":1469824,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:20:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f4fd877594910e2ebe2fb66ee93d582b4d396c66","tid":1469824,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:21:09.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5cda37ca8fd5bb856d3f03d11182e1f976d4ee0e","tid":1469824,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:22:44.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a6585917466b6e674db070bc71a7371d884f9304","tid":1469824,"uid":294052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:24:02.000Z","msg":"我覺得星期一癱瘓到機場除左人數多外 更加因爲擔心警察會係機場清場 類似效果就如721元朗黑夜之後 都有風吹過 黑社會再出發 結果全元朗商鋪一早關門 街上無行人<br />\n出面有個post講過 空管係擔心自身安全下 可以罷工 咁即是對警察既恐慌 會令佢地被動罷工"},{"pid":"612bfd8f61a2b9081ab0776a0ccf903840ac5160","tid":1469824,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:26:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c5d12b034a21d59f1921921d1c41eb890371217f","tid":1469824,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:30:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a637c83aed3e09b079bce1a392cae36dd137df2e","tid":1469824,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:32:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9f237e318eed9fc3c64821ac2fd120d54a3e226d","tid":1469824,"uid":59242,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:32:44.000Z","msg":"岩呀<br />\n楊光話示威者係恐怖主義苗頭，<br />\n就係想國際唔好再支持，再幫就等於支持恐怖分子<br />\n<br />\n所以要繼續做好pr 工作，拎外國輿論支持，攞光環<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5988c4305ea34bb560879e683abacf93fa1cde7e","tid":1469824,"uid":121182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:33:23.000Z","msg":"中共70年來俾外國人講得少？人權問題，一黨專政，佢未驚過， 20年前8964又咪照去！<br />\n<br />\n相反，中國政府同大陸人最憎外國人干涉主權，外國人愈干涉，中國政府就愈強硬，唔會讓步，黑衫間接仲幫埋中國人維穩，因爲大陸人更支持中共，同志們你們看，香港這麼多問題就是沒有走中國特色的社會主義路線，西方那套不行....blah blah blah<br />\n<br />\n中共最怕只係一樣野，就係經濟出現大問題，大陸人就會作反，反對共黨統治，維穩變得困難，但係我地無力影響中國經濟"},{"pid":"d2521bb11a3f1bb